ed;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際學校</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d894b5ad388c29a4bc1d1089b010bf0ffb25b10","tid":1170454,"uid":152548,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"國際學校學生日日返學玩下遊戲，同啲鬼佬老師吹下水，假期時成班friend去坐下daddy隻遊艇，再去賽馬會食返個buffet。考公開試時輕鬆地屈鬼仔機，再入Ivy League/Oxbridge準備做醫生律師ibanker，再唔係就返daddy公司做準CEO。<br />\n<br />\n另邊廂，本地學校學生中一開始已寒窗苦讀，返學被迫操TSA、DSE pastpaper，放學後立刻趕到補習社繼續操。跟住有一日突然被告知DSE又改咗制，之前所付出嘅努力都徒勞無功。終於辛辛苦苦地讀完六年，入到三大，畢業後先發現原來冇加底嘅自己根本就搵唔到好工，注定成世都輸比班國際學校嘅學生。"},{"pid":"17b830f19bc7b5ab019d3d67052580a60b22a008","tid":1170454,"uid":221509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔想仔女讀書讀到跳樓自殺"},{"pid":"c728a105ddeef92d13309c5d7bd5d1963bc728d5","tid":1170454,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bd1eb9b580d2dfbb5bde4e8207a7d6dedbe1681","tid":1170454,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T18:37:40.000Z",